9. Research Prototype Status

The Software is a research prototype. It does not claim to be artificial general
intelligence, autonomous AGI, self-aware, production-ready, procurement-ready,
safety-certified, security-certified, compliance-certified, model-certified,
operationally approved, government-approved, defense-approved, institutionally
approved, or suitable for deployment.

IX-BlackFox-Cognition is intended to explore governed cognition, evidence-bound
planning, memory quarantine, role-separated model review, self-improvement
proposals, BlackFox-compatible handoff, and human-authorized AI-assisted
engineering workflows. It does not grant autonomous authority.

